Module nbbrd.picocsv
Package nbbrd.picocsv

Class Csv.Format

  • java.lang.Object
    • nbbrd.picocsv.Csv.Format
  • Enclosing class:
    Csv
    public static final class Csv.Format
extends Object
    CSV format. This format is used both by reader and writer but is independent of the source of data (stream or files). Therefore, it doesn't deal with encoding.

    This class is immutable and is created by a builder. 

     Csv.Format tsv = Csv.Format.builder().delimiter('\t').build();
